message: I'm excited to offer you this amazing product, and I think you'll love it. I'm willing to let it go for $16000. What do you think?
I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of $13000. Would you be willing to consider that?
I understand you're looking for a good deal, but I'm not sure I can go as low as $13000. I'm willing to meet you in the middle at $14500. What do you think?
I appreciate your willingness to meet me in the middle, but I'm still a bit above my budget. Would you be willing to go down to $13500?
